parameters: \nc<>Old man> Oh, hey, what is this mess! We didn't do anything!

\ncDon't play dumb, old man! You were the one who made the
first move, right?!

\ncWell, there's a possibility that I don't know. Either way,
it doesn't matter.
\nc<Bad Uncle>They're a valuable hostage. Take them with you carefully.
\nc<>What, what should we do, Kei-san?! The, the aunties...!
\nc<>Calm down, Sachiko-chan. I can hear voices.

\ncYou're slow, girl. If you obediently follow, I won't kill
you.
\nc<Bad Member>Yes, there won't be any killing... hehehe...
\nc<>I actually have a black belt in karate.

\nc<>To believe in this... This child is also amazing in various
ways.

\nc<>Actually, I'm just lightly using strengthening magic. But I
feel a strange sense of guilt...

\nc<>Ahem! Anyway, if it's just one guy, we can handle it
somehow.
\nc<>Let's go help everyone, the ordinary believers, for now.
